        wait to see you
        {{#if (eq role "ORGANIZER")}}create and manage amazing events{{else}}explore
          and join exciting events{{/if}}.
      </p>

      <div class="highlight">
        <p><strong>Your account is now active.</strong></p>
        <p>
          <strong>Role:</strong>
          {{role}}
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        As a
        <strong>{{role}}</strong>, you can
        {{#if (eq role "ORGANIZER")}}start creating events, manage attendees,
          and grow your community.{{else}}browse upcoming events, register, and
          connect with organizers and other participants.{{/if}}
      </p>

      <a
        href="https://your-platform-url.com/login"
        class="cta-btn"
        style="color:#fff"
      >Go to Your Dashboard</a>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always
        here to help.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top:24px;">
        Cheers,<br />
        <strong>The Event Management Platform Team</strong>
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
